=head1 NAME

S328WCA - Collects Oracle WebCenter Analytics Information

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This module collects Oracle WebCenter Analytics-related information. The
module covers Oracle WebCenter Analytics Release 10.3.x and later.

The following reports can be generated and are regrouped under C<Oracle
WebCenter Analytics>:

=head1 REPORTS

=cut

echo tput('bold'),'Processing WCA module ...',tput('off')

# Initialization
var $TAIL     = getSetting('RDA_TAIL',1000)
var $WCA_HOME = getSetting('WCA_HOME','')

var $TOC = '%TOC%'
var $TOP = '[[#Top][Back to top]]'
pretoc '1:Oracle WebCenter Analytics'

# Load the common macros
run library()

=head2 Configuration Files

Gathers Oracle WebCenter Analytics-related configuration files.

=cut

debug ' Inside WCA module, collecting the configuration files'
pretoc '2:Configuration Files'
call sort_files(3,0,\
                catFile($WCA_HOME,'pthome.xml'),\
                catFile($WCA_HOME,'settings','configuration.xml'),\
                catFile($WCA_HOME,'settings','portal','portalconfig.xml'))
unpretoc

=head2 Log Files

Gathers Oracle WebCenter Analytics-related log files.

=cut

debug ' Inside WCA module, collecting the log files'
pretoc '2:Log Files'
call sort_files(3,$TAIL,\
                grepDir(catDir($WCA_HOME,'settings','logs'),'\.log$','ip'))
unpretoc 2

